1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,960
Time seems simple, until you have to measure it.

2
00:00:03,960 --> 00:00:08,200
You must count exactly the seconds that appear on screen.

3
00:00:08,200 --> 00:00:13,680
For this, you will only need your tokens and the terminal lights.

4
00:00:13,680 --> 00:00:18,720
This test has two phases, and in each one you will count a different interval.

5
00:00:18,720 --> 00:00:23,080
When a phase starts, the lights will turn on randomly.

6
00:00:23,080 --> 00:00:26,080
That will be the signal to start counting.

7
00:00:26,160 --> 00:00:31,160
When you think the time is over, pass your token through the terminal.

8
00:00:31,160 --> 00:00:35,640
Every second over or under will add error to the team.

9
00:00:35,640 --> 00:00:40,080
If accumulated error exceeds the limit, the phase will reset.

10
00:00:40,080 --> 00:00:44,800
Remember: not all lights will activate at the same time.

11
00:00:44,800 --> 00:00:46,800
Count carefully.
